name: EncephalitisDisordersSNOMED
title: Encephalitis (Disorders) (SNOMED)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses or problems that represent that the patient has Encephalitis regardless of the clinical presentation of the condition),(Data Element Scope: Diagnoses or problems documented in a clinical record.),(Inclusion Criteria: All disorders or findings related to non disease specific Encephalitis),(Exclusion Criteria: none)
